title: La Cornue Dual Fuel Range C9NN Overview
description:
Buy La Cornue 36 CornuFe 90 Matte Black With Satin Chrome Dual Fuel Range - C9NN - http://www.abt.com/product/81528/La-Cornue-C9NN.html

Features:
Capacity
• 3.81 Cu. Ft.
Gas Burners
• One 17500 BTU central burner 
• Three 12000 BTU burners 
• One 6000 BTU simmer burner (down to 600 BTU) 
• Solid Brass burners equipped with Thermocouple Safety Mechanism
Ovens
• Enameled steel door with glass inner door 
• Electric convection oven featuring seven cooking modes 
• Two convection fans three heating elements 
• One wire rack one large tray equipped with a grill pan one pastry tray
Power and Fuel
• Voltage is 240V 60Hz 16 AMP 
• Each range is shipped with a 4-Prong plug which is to be used with a NEMA 14-50R receptacle 
• Requires properly grounded branch circuit protected by a circuit breaker or time-delay fuse (20 AMP). 
• Gas connection 1/2 inch NPT at rear left-hand side 
• Natural gas range with propane conversion kit included 
• High-Altitude Kit required for elevations above 5000 feet
